stimulus:
In this study, you will be presented with and tested on pairings between objects and scenes.

Content Warning: Please be aware that the images used in this study contain content that may be unpleasant or disturbing, including animal cruelty, bodily injury, death, disasters, drugs, illness, violence, and war. You may exit the study at any point if you wish to do so.

Press the spacebar to begin.

You will be presented with pairs of objects and scenes. Please do your best to remember the pairings.

Press the spacebar to continue.

You will be tested on how well you remember the pairings that you just saw. Please answer the questions to the best of your ability.

Press the spacebar to continue.

You will be presented with objects from the pairings that you just studied. Objects will be surrounded with either a red or green frame.

When the frame around the object is red, please do your best to suppress your memory of the associated scene, and additionally prevent any distracting thoughts from coming into awareness.

When the frame around the object is green, please recall the associated scene in as much detail as possible.

Press the spacebar to practice conducting this task.

The practice portion has concluded. Press the spacebar to continue onto the task.
